Merge pull request #4 from vkrol/patch-1

Fix small typo
Adds Android JS bundle build command to Travis.yml

Reverts back to `index.ios/android.js` files to fix CI builds

We should be able to switch back to a custom index file name after upgrading to the next React Native since there seems to be a new `file-path` argument that may allow us to specify the custom `index.native.js` file.
[Android] Adds app icon & changes app name

[Android] Adds style adjustment for screen

It seems like `alignItems: 'flex-end'` doesn't work like it does in iOS. Also it seems like Android has a minimum `fontWeight` of 400, so I couldn't get it down to look exactly like the iOS app.

[Android] Fixes keyAction button styles

Uses TouchableOpacity for the keyAction buttons since it seems like there is a bug on Android where the `borderRadius` is ignored after the first tap.
